{"tid":17420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家，唔好再打d\"係未\"，\"起邊度\"既錯字","createTime":"2016-12-01T22:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-10T01:15:17.000Z","uid":50263,"like":37,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"554baa3d064b3b0021ff52bd95c0d3d19453de56","tid":17420,"uid":50263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:08:42.000Z","msg":"打正字好難咩？見到都燥，出面一堆「係未」同「起度」做乜撚野？<br />\n唔識字我教埋你啦。「係咪」同「係度」<br />\n衰撚過吾系甘牙。不知所謂。"},{"pid":"c803b003b4ed5a3c41b3d44c40ddd993f6185bda","tid":17420,"uid":46321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:15:23.000Z","msg":"喺道呀渠頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c716bce139d54c19e810542723591df8386705b0","tid":17420,"uid":23744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:17:14.000Z","msg":"係咪用左係度就吾鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96d60a50ee738f2f3f9f591a7320db868613fb4","tid":17420,"uid":50263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺道呀渠頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">先說「邊度」的同義詞「邊處」（音bin1 xu3），望字知意，不懂粵語相信也不難明白。至於「邊度」與「邊道」甚而「焉道」，就要考究「度」與「道」二字，究竟哪個有地方之意。<br />\n<br />\n其實兩字都隱含這個意思，真要考究用哪個才貼近白話文而讓人更易明白，我也分不清。但我初步認為，一般的廣州話詞典都只列「邊度」，該是較為人接受的用法。另外，不查不知道，原來「邊道」除了用作粵語，古今漢語都有固定的用法，可參看網上《漢典》的解釋﹕1. 邊地的官員；2. 道路的兩側部分。百度百科更列有「邊道是鑄幣周緣的側面部分」一說。<br />\n<br />\n既然「邊度」與「邊道」均可，但「邊道」不是方言時，已有其他意思，為免引起不必要誤會，我覺得還是用較為人知的「邊度」為好。至於「焉道」，問題更多，就更不宜採用了。<br />\n<br />\n其實還想到「去到邊食到邊」這句話的「到邊」，再扯下去可能不知到邊處才可收科了</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩上網搵，拿唔同你拗「度」定「道」啦。<br />\n但「起」錯到仆街不知所謂係無庸置疑既，我唔明點解d人可以打出黎。"},{"pid":"48cb78606bec8a7e12d77450364a4fac22c799d1","tid":17420,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:12:38.000Z","msg":"用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b73b80d66560653936705d9cf67f0635814ee6","tid":17420,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"😉"},{"pid":"1c0486cafa58bc4521244c9d4ffd176f985414d7","tid":17420,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟 喺 呢啲字成日要搵好耐先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d05d4754bc6fa357f20a95e220aca402a5ce976","tid":17420,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟 喺 呢啲字成日要搵好耐先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少要禁三四下空白鍵<br />\n<br />\n順便變下禁既正字係咪撳"},{"pid":"b3b23dbb98b2a676d4690001030f9f831c3235b0","tid":17420,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟 喺 呢啲字成日要搵好耐先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少要禁三四下空白鍵<br />\n<br />\n順便<span style=\"color: red;\">問</span>下禁既正字係咪撳</blockquote>"},{"pid":"917f4b63d280057b0be5a2a9ce92a647aa637014","tid":17420,"uid":28335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打正字好難咩？見到都燥，出面一堆「係未」同「起度」做乜撚野？<br />\n唔識字我教埋你啦。「係咪」同「係度」<br />\n衰撚過吾系甘牙。不知所謂。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\