44d0e8f8d9071f6797410a91964dd5d1cfaf762","tid":17420,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打正字好難咩？見到都燥，出面一堆「係未」同「起度」做乜撚野？<br />\n唔識字我教埋你啦。「係咪」同「係度」<br />\n衰撚過吾系甘牙。不知所謂。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「係呀」一定岩<br />\n<br />\n「係邊」就有少少保留<br />\n係點發都發唔到口講果個音, 加口字邊又唔方便打字<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 我用「嚮邊」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係同嚮都講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係邊 嚮邊<br />\n係暑 嚮暑<br />\n係屋企 嚮屋企</blockquote><br />\n我用開「响」邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40dcfe2e334ff831c52ec973bccc69d099821e6","tid":17420,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:48:45.000Z","msg":"啱 嘅"},{"pid":"6925134dd2879019ea34b43052d339fb9d640f6c","tid":17420,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:52:03.000Z","msg":"嗰 啱 嘅"},{"pid":"18464bf055c4e425fce790b2985e09f6fdf998ed","tid":17420,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時都會問人起邊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你起乜撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6db320a0570444dc8daf5c7fdf267d792d2b11","tid":17420,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:58:34.000Z","msg":"依到 呢到 哩到<br />\n??"},{"pid":"00502b192b4b90b0b8e76550432ab7599db6b524","tid":17420,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"係你老母度<br />\n係度同喺度唔同音架<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"10ac62db2f6b4c313b1d0c074dfc028448d33c2b","tid":17420,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:02:02.000Z","msg":"旺角係喺九龍"},{"pid":"3b2cd589124d07425bd85cfd867d044277210598","tid":17420,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-