\n<br />\n每次錯字post都見到師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18fe9c7c2f634908525b7fcfa0e280831dfee3b","tid":17420,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家留意番個重點， 係講緊「起」同「未」啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪<br />\n喺邊度"},{"pid":"f760b6c12b945905f97cf8f5431aaca52b1bbaa0","tid":17420,"uid":59344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:12:02.000Z","msg":"好撚憎見到人咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1439b2903e9581e5e8dc674ea76ba5880a4d970e","tid":17420,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:14:14.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;呢家&rdquo; 先最難頂，屌你邊到鄉下可以發到呢個音，依家/而家都可以接受，&ldquo;呢家&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cc84d23fc3bf853b82a9e61b7e7781fb8a26a2","tid":17420,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:14:16.000Z","msg":"上呢啲咁唔正經嘅論壇，<br />\n仲要人用正經字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba66074f4a50ea2c98a5bdefcff6964cfc1bbce7","tid":17420,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「係呀」一定岩<br />\n<br />\n「係邊」就有少少保留<br />\n係點發都發唔到口講果個音, 加口字邊又唔方便打字<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 我用「嚮邊」</blockquote><br />\n岩你老母</blockquote><br />\nOn9打岩都要屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一向 啱喺嚟嗰嘅 呢幾個字大家知打速度係會難搵啲<br />\n打少個口字邊都唔會屌啦<br />\n有時個人變通下好冇<br />\n打 吾系禾刀 呢啲5p字就真係要嚴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係速成，唔係速度呀"},{"pid":"78f2b5e69ed4b3e9b1d0ef801607b089cef2c4e0","tid":17420,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依到 呢到 哩到<br />\n??</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f28e4fe7f9976e7d473133fbf4cdfbdc77689eb1","tid":17420,"uid":10454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d761caa645e37b922ffbec718106a71ed6098a","tid":17420,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:41:54.000Z","msg":"一直用喺到 原來都錯到仆街<br />\n會用返度㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">死啦我又唔記得係用返定用翻定係用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"bce0e8b78f7e00de9bda2d5446124b324d7a69d3","tid":17420,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"見過有人打「仲乜」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗「做乜」9"},{"pid":"9a6a92f6d4bbad99a972a0f4ad35e8de941c6b78","tid":17420,"uid":50795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"只有幾個小問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 用書面語要規範無問題，點解我手寫我口既粵語都要規範？<br />\n<br />\n2. 邊個有權力規範？係咪會搵返正字黎規範？<br />\n<br />\n3. 你確定「起邊」係錯？你試下讀一次依個詞，會發現口型都唔洗轉，就可讀到出黎，讀「係」邊會因為收開口，連住讀重唇既「邊」會唔順，所以一直有人會讀「起邊」，尤見於上一輩。"},{"pid":"f74306af8a5f8d394fb07c2805b47bf1d0ef9b66","tid":17420,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上呢啲咁唔正經嘅論壇，<br />\n仲要人用正經字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n宜家又唔係考試<br />\n咁著緊正唔正字有乜為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bce654d929487c04f565a3e1ca7125afcf45cea","tid":17420,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直用喺到 原來都錯到仆街<br />\n會用返度㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">死啦我又唔記得係用返定用翻定係用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://words.hk/zidin/v/19169/返/番\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwords.hk%2Fzidin%2Fv%2F19169%2F%E8%BF%94%2F%E7%95%AA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2df18e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://words.hk/zidin/v/19169/返/番</a><br />\n<br />\nsame"},{"pid":"551261d5b041cd787613018e5a334f3bd45f3a8c","tid":17420,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟 喺 呢啲字成日要搵好耐先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少要禁三四下空白鍵<br />\n<br />\n順便變下禁既正字係咪撳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想正經同習慣用正字，最好用返倉頡。</blockquote><br />\n乜最好用番倉頡<br />\n依家係講方便<br />\n要記哂幾個碼你估個個都咁易學倉頡?<br />\n唔駛搵字根本係quick快 打得多自己會記得d 位<br />\n5p個d係玩野字<br />\n呢d係for方便<br />\n咪糾枉過正啦屌"},{"pid":"a1b6de10dbcf601b7983dbd44c79eda30a91ff40","tid":17420,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T01:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只有幾個小問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 用書面語要規範無問題，點解我手寫我口既粵語都要規範？<br />\n<br />\n2. 邊個有權力規範？係咪會搵返正字黎規範？<br />\n<br />\n3. 你確定「起邊」係錯？你試下讀一次依個詞，會發現口型都唔洗轉，就可讀到出黎，讀「係」邊會因為收開口，連住讀重唇既「邊」會唔順，所以一直有人會讀「起邊」，尤見於上一輩。</blockquote><br />\n睇番d粵語殘片既script 就會發現起邊根本大把人用<br />\n樓豬呢d當自己係專家係準則"},{"pid":"ab85943dd4816e60fd521f96a05f24bc34490164","tid":17420,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:08:31.000Z","msg":"起mean"},{"pid":"2caa9387521d693e0bee1dcf4a7d90a0c1b112ce","tid":17420,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:29:06.000Z","msg":"「咪臭係」<br />\n<br />\n明明就係「咪就係」<br />\n真係想知打「咪臭係」嘅人平時日常口語係咪都係咁讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44573a56193230ebfe9eb27d0fd7819c53065fb3","tid":17420,"uid":32890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開度 但係個喺字好麻煩 廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚟 喺 呢啲字成日要搵好耐先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少要禁三四下空白鍵<br />\n<br />\n順便變下禁既正字係咪撳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想正經同習慣用正字，最好用返倉頡。</blockquote><br />\n我手機同電腦都係用倉頡<br />\n唔知點解手機打 喺 嘅 㗎 呢啲字好方便<br />\n但反而電腦個倉頡有時同返同一個倉頡碼都冇&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n所以好多時候用電腦都直接打 係 既 架 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca7e762173b2b4fec3ded1621070138b45bad53","tid":17420,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"以經 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca23fcbc4184cef3fac73c3498a6c8cdb36b0766","tid":17420,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前喺廢登成日見人打「邊到」「以經」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話佢哋又屌返你轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老母就廢登</blockquote><br />\n你老母高登連香港字都出唔到唔廢啊?! 一版load幾十秒唔廢啊? 咁鍾意高登返去幫林祖舜奶袋底啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c834c937fa3713edee41396edc6bad3fadbf80","tid":17420,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「咪臭係」<br />\n<br />\n明明就係「咪就係」<br />\n真係想知打「咪臭係」嘅人平時日常口語係咪都係咁讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n佢哋想玩「咪&quot;臭閪&quot;」嘅諧音"}]}